I'm Jeremy

Hey there! I'm a data specialist who loves taking the lead on projects that make a difference. I have several years of experience in process automation and business intelligence, which I draw from to bring all kinds of valuable insights to the table through analytics and visualization. One of my biggest strengths is coming up with innovative ways to turn raw data into a real advantage for organizations across an array of industries.
